    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760150/extras/884f40bd03805d8aa66773f00438d111.poster.avif?t=1707806406\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760150/extras/884f40bd03805d8aa66773f00438d111.webm?t=1707806406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760150/extras/884f40bd03805d8aa66773f00438d111.mp4?t=1707806406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Addicting gunplay and movement</h2>Move smoothly with sliding and slide jumping and shoot headshots with first shot accuracy. We have taken inspiration from hardcore and casual shooters alike and combined hipfire and aim down sights playstyles.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760150/extras/a35b271557d3633c060cebf053d2de87.poster.avif?t=1707806406\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760150/extras/a35b271557d3633c060cebf053d2de87.webm?t=1707806406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760150/extras/a35b271557d3633c060cebf053d2de87.mp4?t=1707806406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gear up</h2>Buy and upgrade you gear during missions. Unlock even more gear and upgrades in the Player Hub.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760150/extras/7447da07dfda966f6cab314671618253.poster.avif?t=1707806406\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760150/extras/7447da07dfda966f6cab314671618253.webm?t=1707806406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1760150/extras/7447da07dfda966f6cab314671618253.mp4?t=1707806406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless fun</h2>Survive endless rounds of zombies which get tougher every round. You can play solo or up to 4 players.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Map variety</h2>Play multiple maps of three different styles: <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Main maps</strong> are large-scale maps focusing mainly on gameplay with story elements and many secrets to be found.<br></li><li><strong>Survival maps</strong> are smaller scale maps focusing purely on gameplay and survival with some small secrets.<br></li><li><strong>Challenge maps</strong> are tiny maps with unique mechanics or objectives.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Always-OFFline</h2>Realm of the Undead can be played offline, LAN or online.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NO microtransactions</h2>Realm of the Undead will <strong>not</strong> feature any microtransactions and all items are unlocked through <strong>gameplay only</strong>.",
